    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel Crisis: Paper Marking Affected",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Second Phase of Paper Marking for the G. C. E Ordinary Level Examination was suspended temporarily due to the fuel crisis in the country.",
        "Commissioner General of Examination L. M. D. Dharmasena said that Phase One of Paper Marking was completed on a successful note.",
        "2021 A/Level Practical Examinations for engineering technology is currently underway.",
        "Examinations Commissioner General said that practical examinations will be conducted until the 10th of July.",
        "Accordingly, Examinations Commissioner General L.M.D Dharmasena said that A/Level examination results will be released by the end of July or within the 1st two weeks of August."
      ],
